description: The Ethernet Network Diagnostics Cluster provides a means to acquire standardized diagnostics metrics that MAY be used by a Node to assist a user or Administrator in diagnosing potential prob­ lems. The Ethernet Network Diagnostics Cluster attempts to centralize all metrics that are relevant to a potential Ethernet connection to a Node.
